Required:
* sudo aptitude install libboost-dev
* sudo aptitude install libfcgi-dev
* patched cgic205
* libmemcached
* memcacheq

mkdir /var/lock/BeerCrush (not necessary?)

Build server(s):
--------------------
Copy some files to /var/www
Create some symlinks to the app source
Make/verify config files
Install spread toolkit
Set up spread daemons
Install and run queue processor script
mkdir /var/run/BeerCrush

MemcacheQ server(s):
--------------------
Install spread toolkit
Start memcacheq

CouchDB server(s):
--------------------
Install and configure couchdb
Configure replication between servers

Web server(s):
--------------------
Install apache2.2 + PHP
Configure OAK conf
